cs.CR, cs.SI, cs.SD, cs.CY, cs.SE 

This paper discusses the security issues related to online social networks and proposes a method based on social honeypots to detect and filter malicious profiles. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). Other likely categories include cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), cs.SD (Software Engineering), cs.CY (Computers and Society), and cs.SE (Software Engineering).
